<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" 
	href="<%=path%>/a00_com/a00_com.css">
</head>
<%--
	3) 화면 UI 변경
		물건명 : [    ]
		가격 :[    ] ~ [    ]
